orph lets you cast a card face down by paying {3}, and lets you turn the face-down permanent face up any time you have priority by paying its morph cost."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"The face-down spell has no mana cost and has a converted mana cost of 0. When you cast a face-down spell, put it on the stack face down so no other player knows what it is, and pay {3}. This is an alternative cost."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"When the spell resolves, it enters the battlefield as a 2/2 creature with no name, mana cost, creature types, or abilities. It’s colorless and has a converted mana cost of 0. Other effects that apply to the creature can still grant it any of these characteristics."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"Any time you have priority, you may turn the face-down creature face up by revealing what its morph cost is and paying that cost. This is a special action. It doesn’t use the stack and can’t be responded to. Only a face-down permanent can be turned face up this way; a face-down spell cannot."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"Because the permanent is on the battlefield both before and after it’s turned face up, turning a permanent face up doesn’t cause any enters-the-battlefield abilities to trigger."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"A permanent that turns face up or face down changes characteristics but is otherwise the same permanent. Spells and abilities that were targeting that permanent, as well as Auras and Equipment that were attached to the permanent, aren’t affected."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"At any time, you can look at a face-down spell or permanent you control. You can’t look at face-down spells or permanents you don’t control unless an effect instructs you to do so."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"You must ensure that your face-down spells and permanents can easily be differentiated from each other. You’re not allowed to mix up the cards that represent them on the battlefield in order to confuse other players. The order they entered the battlefield should remain clear. Common methods for doing this include using markers or dice, or simply placing them in order on the battlefield."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"If a face-down permanent leaves the battlefield, you must reveal it. You must also reveal all face-down spells and permanents you control if you leave the game or if the game ends."}],"foreignNames":[{"name":"Sagu-Bogenschütze","text":"Reichweite (Diese Kreatur kann fliegende Kreaturen blocken.)\nMorph {4}{G} (Du kannst diese Karte verdeckt für {3} als eine 2/2 Kreatur wirken. Decke sie zu einem beliebigen Zeitpunkt für ihre Morph-Kosten auf.)","type":"Kreatur — Naga, Bogenschütze","flavor":"Das Sirren seiner Pfeile erinnert an das Zischen einer Schlange.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387453&type=card","language":"German","multiverseid":387453},{"name":"Arquero de Sagu","text":"Alcance. (Esta criatura puede bloquear a criaturas con la habilidad de volar.)\nMetamorfosis {4}{G}. (Puedes lanzar esta carta boca abajo como una criatura 2/2 pagando {3}. Ponla boca arriba en cualquier momento pagando su coste de metamorfosis.)","type":"Criatura — Arquero naga","flavor":"Sus flechas silban como serpientes.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=389336&type=card","language":"Spanish","multiverseid":389336},{"name":"Archer de Sagu","text":"Portée (Cette créature peut bloquer les créatures avec le vol.)\nMue {4}{G} (Vous pouvez lancer cette carte face cachée comme une créature 2/2 pour {3}. Retournez-la à tout moment pour son coût de mue.)","type":"Créature : naga et archer","flavor":"Ses flèches sifflent comme un serpent.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387722&type=card","language":"French","multiverseid":387722},{"name":"Arciere di Sagu","text":"Raggiungere (Questa creatura può bloccare le creature con volare.)\nMetamorfosi {4}{G} (Puoi lanciare questa carta a faccia in giù come una creatura 2/2 pagando {3}. Girala a faccia in su in qualsiasi momento pagando il suo costo di metamorfosi.)","type":"Creatura — Arciere Naga","flavor":"Le sue frecce fischiano come il sibilo di un serpente.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387991&type=card","language":"Italian","multiverseid":387991},{"name":"サグの射手","text":"到達（このクリーチャーは飛行を持つクリーチャーをブロックできる。）\n変異{4}{G}（あなたはこのカードを、{3}で２/２クリーチャーとして裏向きに唱えてもよい。これの変異コストで、これをいつでも表向きにしてよい。）","type":"クリーチャー — ナーガ・射手","flavor":"彼の放つ矢は、大蛇の威嚇音のような音をたてながら飛翔する。","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388260&type=card","language":"Japanese","multiverseid":388260},{"name":"사구 궁수","text":"대공 (이 생물은 비행을 가진 생물을 방어할 수 있다.)\n변이 {4}{G} (당신은 {3}을 지불해서 이 카드를 뒷면 상태의 2/2 생물로 발동할 수 있다. 언제든지 변이 비용을 지불하고 앞면이 보이도록 뒤집을 수 있다.)","type":"생물 — 나가 궁수","flavor":"그의 화살은 이무기의 울음소리와 비슷한 소리를 낸다.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388529&type=card","language":"Korean","multiverseid":388529},{"name":"Arqueiro de Sagu","text":"Alcance (Esta criatura pode bloquear criaturas com voar.)\nMetamorfose {4}{G} (Você pode conjurar este card com a face voltada para baixo como uma criatura 2/2 por {3}. Volte sua face para cima a qualquer momento pagando seu custo de metamorfose.)","type":"Criatura — Naga Arqueiro","flavor":"Sua flecha sibila como uma serpente.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388798&type=card","language":"Portuguese (Brazil)","multiverseid":388798},{"name":"Лучник из Сагу","text":"Захват (Это существо может блокировать существа с Полетом.)\nОборотень {4}{G} (Вы можете разыграть эту карту рубашкой вверх как существо 2/2 за {3}. Переверните ее рубашкой вниз в любой момент за ее стоимость Оборотня.)","type":"Существо — Нага Лучник","flavor":"Его стрелы шипят, словно сердитая змея.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=389067&type=card","language":"Russian","multiverseid":389