egality":"Legal"},{"format":"Pauper","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Penny","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Pioneer","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Premodern","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Standard","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Vintage","legality":"Legal"}],"id":"be22b604-ef97-586a-8870-857be59e59d1"},{"name":"Bitter Revelation","manaCost":"{3}{B}","cmc":4.0,"colors":["Black"],"colorIdentity":["B"],"type":"Sorcery","types":["Sorcery"],"rarity":"Common","set":"KTK","setName":"Khans of Tarkir","text":"Look at the top four cards of your library. Put two of them into your hand and the rest into your graveyard. You lose 2 life.","flavor":"\"Here you lie then, Ugin. The corpses of worlds will join you in the tomb.\"\n—Sorin Markov","artist":"Viktor Titov","number":"65","layout":"normal","multiverseid":"386489","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=386489&type=card","foreignNames":[{"name":"Bittere Offenbarung","text":"Schaue dir die obersten vier Karten deiner Bibliothek an. Nimm zwei davon auf deine Hand und lege den Rest auf deinen Friedhof. Du verlierst 2 Lebenspunkte.","type":"Hexerei","flavor":"„Hier liegst du also, Ugin. Die Trümmer ganzer Welten werden dir im Grab Gesellschaft leisten.\" —Sorin Markov","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387296&type=card","language":"German","multiverseid":387296},{"name":"Revelación amarga","text":"Mira las cuatro primeras cartas de tu biblioteca. Pon dos de ellas en tu mano y el resto en tu cementerio. Pierdes 2 vidas.","type":"Conjuro","flavor":"\"Así que aquí yaces, Ugin. Los cadáveres de varios mundos te acompañarán en la tumba\". —Sorin Markov","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=389179&type=card","language":"Spanish","multiverseid":389179},{"name":"Amère révélation","text":"Regardez les quatre cartes du dessus de votre bibliothèque. Mettez deux d'entre elles dans votre main et le reste dans votre cimetière. Vous perdez 2 points de vie.","type":"Rituel","flavor":"« C'est donc ici que tu reposes, Ugin. Les dépouilles des mondes te rejoindront dans la tombe. » —Sorin Markov","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387565&type=card","language":"French","multiverseid":387565},{"name":"Amara Rivelazione","text":"Guarda le prime quattro carte del tuo grimorio. Aggiungine due alla tua mano e metti le altre nel tuo cimitero. Perdi 2 punti vita.","type":"Stregoneria","flavor":"\"Dunque è qui che giaci, Ugin. I cadaveri di molti mondi ti seguiranno nella tomba.\" —Sorin Markov","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387834&type=card","language":"Italian","multiverseid":387834},{"name":"苦々しい天啓","text":"あなたのライブラリーの一番上から４枚のカードを見る。そのうち２枚をあなたの手札に加え、残りをあなたの墓地に置く。あなたは２点のライフを失う。","type":"ソーサリー","flavor":"「ここに眠るか、ウギンよ。じきに世界の遺体がお前とともにこの墓に葬られることになるだろう。」 ――ソリン・マルコフ","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388103&type=card","language":"Japanese","multiverseid":388103},{"name":"씁쓸한 깨달음","text":"당신의 서고 맨 위의 카드 네 장을 본다. 그 중 두 장을 당신의 손으로 가져가고 나머지는 당신의 무덤에 넣는다. 당신은 생명 2점을 잃는다.","type":"집중마법","flavor":"\"우진, 이곳에 잠들어 있었구나. 이제 모든 차원의 시체들이 네 곁을 지킬 것이다.\" —소린 마르코프","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388372&type=card","language":"Korean","multiverseid":388372},{"name":"Revelação Amarga","text":"Olhe os quatro cards do topo do seu grimório. Coloque dois deles em sua mão e o restante em seu cemitério. Você perde 2 pontos de vida.","type":"Feitiço","flavor":"\"Então aqui está você, Ugin. Os cadáveres de mundos inteiros se juntarão a você no túmulo.\" — Sorin Markov","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388641&type=card","language":"Portuguese (Brazil)","multiverseid":388641},{"name":"Горькое Осознание","text":"Посмотрите четыре верхние карты вашей библиотеки. Положите две из них в вашу руку, а остальные — на ваше кладбище. Вы теряете 2 жизни.","type":"Волшебство","flavor":"«Вот где ты покоишься, Уджин. Трупы целых миров скоро лягут с тобой в одну могилу». — Сорин Марков","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=388910&type=card","language":"Russian","multiverseid":388910},{"name":"苦涩启示","text":"检视你牌库顶的四张牌。将其中两张置于你手上，其余的牌则置入你的坟墓场。你失去2点生命。","type":"法术","flavor":"「乌金，原来你沉眠于此。众世界的残骸也将到墓中与你相聚。」 ～索霖马可夫","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=386758&type=card","language":"Chinese Simplified","multiverseid":386758},{"name":"苦澀啟示","text":"檢視你牌庫頂的四張牌。將其中兩張置於你手上，其餘的牌則置入你的墳墓場。你失去2點生命。","type":"巫術","flavor":"「烏金，原來你沉眠於此。眾世界的殘骸也將到墓中與你相聚。」 ～索霖馬可夫","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387027&type=card","language":"Chinese Traditional","multiverseid":387027}],"printings":["CMR","KTK","MB1"],"originalText":"Look at the top four cards of your library. Put two of them into your hand and the rest into your graveyard. You lose 2 life.","originalType":"Sorcery","legalities":[{"format":"Commander","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Duel","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Legacy","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Modern","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Pauper","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Penny","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Pioneer","legality":"Legal"},{"format":"Vintage","legality":"Legal"}],"id":"0a499de7-798f-5cc5-bb42-434e0ec6f340"},{"name":"Sidisi's Pet","manaCost":"{3}{B}","cmc":4.0,"colors":["Black"],"colorIdentity":["B"],"type":"Creature — Zombie Ape","types":["Creature"],"subtypes":["Zombie","Ape"],"rarity":"Common","set":"KTK","setName":"Khans of Tarkir","text":"Lifelink (Damage dealt by this creature also causes you to gain that much life.)\nMorph {1}{B} (You may cast this card face down as a 2/2 creature for {3}. Turn it face up any time for its morph cost.)","flavor":"The Sultai distinguish between pet and slave by the material of the chain.","artist":"Evan Shipard","number":"90","power":"1","toughness":"4","layout":"normal","multiverseid":"386665","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=386665&type=card","watermark":"sultai","rulings":[{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"Morph lets you cast a card face down by paying {3}, and lets you turn the face-down permanent face up any time you have priority by paying its morph cost."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"The face-down spell has no mana cost and has a converted mana cost of 0. When you cast a face-down spell, put it on the stack face down so no other player knows what it is, and pay {3}. This is an alternative cost."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"When the spell resolves, it enters the battlefield as a 2/2 creature with no name, mana cost, creature types, or abilities. It’s colorless and has a converted mana cost of 0. Other effects that apply to the creature can still grant it any of these characteristics."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"Any time you have priority, you may turn the face-down creature face up by revealing what its morph cost is and paying that cost. This is a special action. It doesn’t use the stack and can’t be responded to. Only a face-down permanent can be turned face up this way; a face-down spell cannot."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"Because the permanent is on the battlefield both before and after it’s turned face up, turning a permanent face up doesn’t cause any enters-the-battlefield abilities to trigger."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"A permanent that turns face up or face down changes characteristics but is otherwise the same permanent. Spells and abilities that were targeting that permanent, as well as Auras and Equipment that were attached to the permanent, aren’t affected."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"At any time, you can look at a face-down spell or permanent you control. You can’t look at face-down spells or permanents you don’t control unless an effect instructs you to do so."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"You must ensure that your face-down spells and permanents can easily be differentiated from each other. You’re not allowed to mix up the cards that represent them on the battlefield in order to confuse other players. The order they entered the battlefield should remain clear. Common methods for doing this include using markers or dice, or simply placing them in order on the battlefield."},{"date":"2014-09-20","text":"If a face-down permanent leaves the battlefield, you must reveal it. You must also reveal all face-down spells and permanents you control if you leave the game or if the game ends."}],"foreignNames":[{"name":"Sidisis Schoßtier","text":"Lebensverknüpfung (Schaden, der von dieser Kreatur zugefügt wird, lässt dich ebenso viele Lebenspunkte dazuerhalten.)\nMorph {1}{B} (Du kannst diese Karte verdeckt für {3} als eine 2/2 Kreatur wirken. Decke sie zu einem beliebigen Zeitpunkt für ihre Morph-Kosten auf.)","type":"Kreatur — Zombie, Menschenaffe","flavor":"Die Sultai unterscheiden zwischen Schoßtier und Sklave anhand des Materials seiner Kette.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=387472&type=card","language":"German","multiverseid":387472},{"name":"Mascota de Sidisi","text":"Vínculo vital. (El daño hecho por esta criatura también hace que ganes esa misma cantidad de vidas.)\nMetamorfosis {1}{B}. (Puedes lanzar esta carta boca abajo como una criatura 2/2 pagando {3}. Ponla boca arriba en cualquier momento pagando su coste de metamorfosis.)","type":"Criatura — Simio zombie","flavor":"Los Sultai distinguen entre mascota y esclavo por el material de la cadena.","imageUrl":"http://gatherer.wizards.com/Handlers/Image.ashx?multiverseid=389355&type=card","language":"Spanish","multiverseid":389355},{"name":"Mascotte de Sidisi","text":"Lien de vie (Les blessures infligées par cette créature vous font aussi gagner autant de points de vie.)\nMue {1}{B} (Vous pouvez lancer cette carte face cachée comme une créature 2/2 pour {3}. Retournez-la à tout moment pour son coût de mue.)","type":"Créature : zombie 